==Soccer==
=== 2024 NCAA Championship win by the Vermont Catamounts ===
On December 16th 2024, the University of Vermont Catamounts Men&#x27;s Soccer team defeated the Marshall University Thundering Herd in the 2024 NCAA Division I men&#x27;s soccer tournament championship game to claim the 2024 College Cup. This marks the first national championship by any America East Conference team in league history.

