** The film&#x27;s narrator
** Mr. Chang, the owner of Dukesberry&#x27;s local Chinese restaurant
* Kevin Nealon as Mayor Dewey
** James Barbour provides his singing voice
* Carmen Filpi as a homeless man
* Norm Crosby as the judge
* Jon Lovitz as Tom Baltezor

